Keyboard Short-cuts
-------------------
Full Screen Shot - Command shift 3
Partial Screen Shot - Command shift 4
Specific window - Command shift 4 spacebar
Search bar - Command space

Track Pad - Gestures
--------------------
Finder - System Preferences - Track Pad
Tap once - Single click
Two fingers tap - secondary select
Three finger lookup - word dictionary lookup
Three finger drag - drags current window
Two finger scroll - direction scrolling
Two finger pinch - zoom in zoom out
Two finger rotate - rotate selection
Two finger swipe - swipe left/right
Three Finger swipe - Full screen swipe
Four Finger Swipe up - Mission Control
Three Finger Pitch - Launch Pad
Three Finger Spread - Show Desktop

Setup Hot Corners
-----------------
Finder - system preference - mission control - hot corners

Batch Rename
------------
highlight all files - right click or double finger
then select rename (x) items on sidebar menu

Air Drop file sharing
---------------------
ipad - swipe up - select airdrop
on imac - command shift R
drag and drop

LauchPad
--------
F4 or select the rocket icon on the dock
click on app or start typing the name of the app
To group apps - drop one on top of another

Software Installation
---------------------
Once downloaded in finder drag the application icon to the "Applications" entry on the right

Terminal
--------
Command T - new terminal
Command W - close a terminal
Command D - open them up side be side
Command [ - toggle between terminals

Installing - Homebrew installer
-------------------------------
xcode-select --install
www.brew.sh
copy command on webpage
run it in a terminal
brew help
brew cask

Show hidden files
-----------------
from terminal
defaults write com.apple.finder AppleShowFiles TRUE;
right click finder - reload

Install Sublime Text Editor
---------------------------
brew install Caskroom/versions/sublime-text3

Install Google Hangouts
-----------------------
brew cask install google-hangouts

Install Slack & Skype
---------------------
brew cask install slack
brew cask install skype

Install Java SDK
----------------
brew cask install java

Install Maven & Ant
-------------------
brew install maven
brew install ant

Install Ruby
------------
curl -sSL https://get.rvm.io | bash -s stable
copy the "source" from the displayed text
rvm install 2.3.0
rvm list
rvm usr ruby-2.3.0

Install GIT
-----------
brew install git
install sourcetree for GUI to Git

Install MongoDB 
----------------
brew cask install mongodb
for mongo install robomongo client

Install Xcode
-------------
From the AppStore

For MySQL use Sequel Pro GUI
----------------------------

Hadoop Learning VM
------------------
www.cloudera.com
once started - user cloudera password cloudera
localhost:8088/cluster
hortonworks.com/downloads 
localhost:8888

SSH 
---
ssh-keygen -t rsa -C "email address"
id_rsa - private
id_rsa.pub - public

Create a voice file
-------------------
say -v Fred -o test.mp4 "Hello World! I'm now talking to you"
play the mp4 file ! (lots of voices to choose from)

